[[File:SquidLake-ROTS.png|thumb|250px|''Squid Lake'']]
'''Mon Calamari Ballet''' was a prestigious aquatic dance troupe that performed the show [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] in the [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]<ref name="SWCE">{{CSWECite|II|326|Mon Calamari Ballet}}</ref> in [[19 BBY/Legends|19 BBY]].<ref name="NEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref> [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] viewed their performance<ref name="SWCE" /> alongside others.<ref name="RotS">{{Film|III}}</ref>

